    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Doujutsu)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 2</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 3</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 19</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> E, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>This technique can be used in one of two ways:<br><br>Sharingan Mirage (Requires Glare (a)): The subject falls @Condition[unconscious]{unconscious} for 1d6+1 rounds, after which it is @Condition[dazed;duration=1]{dazed} for 1 round. The subject will lose all memory from 1 round before it fell unconscious to when it became @Condition[dazed]{dazed}, except highly impactful events.<br><br>Technique Copy: You gain a gaze attack, which increases the success chance of your Ninja's Mimicry abilities against any creature affected by the gaze attack (no save, is avoided completely by a creature using avert one's gaze).</p>\n\n\n\n",
